  "prompt": "How can an Indian engineer find jobs in Israel?",
  "response": "Here are several ways an Indian engineer can find jobs in Israel:\n\n1. Online Job Portals\n- LinkedIn\n- Glassdoor\n- Indeed Israel\n- JobInfo.co.il\n- Israeli startup job websites\n\n2. Professional Networks\n- Tech conferences and events\n- Professional networking groups\n- Alumni networks\n- Industry-specific LinkedIn groups\n\n3. Company Direct Applications\n- Research Israeli tech companies\n- Apply directly through company websites\n- Focus on companies in:\n  - High-tech sector\n  - Cybersecurity\n  - Software development\n  - AI/Machine Learning\n  - Electronics\n\n4. Recruitment Agencies\n- Specialized tech recruitment agencies\n- International recruitment firms with Israel operations\n\n5. Government/Bilateral Programs\n- Check Indo-Israeli technology cooperation programs\n- Look for work visa sponsorship opportunities\n\n6. Skill Requirements\n- Strong technical skills\n- Proficiency in English\n- Knowledge of Hebrew is beneficial\n- Updated resume/CV\n- Professional certifications\n\n7. Work Visa Process\n- Obtain work permit\n- Apply for relevant visa (work/professional)\n- Meet Israeli immigration requirements\n\n8. Startup Ecosystem\n- Focus on Israeli startup ecosystem\n- Attend startup events and hackathons\n\nNetworking and persistent job search are key strategies.",
